==============================================

Current implementation runs HVAC at full power whenever temperature deviates
from setpoint by more than 0.5°C, regardless of electricity pricing.

Peak hours (12:00-17:00): $0.15/kWh
Off-peak hours: $0.08-0.10/kWh

Total baseline cost: $52.80
